      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DASHING DARLEY (5) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Other three back before a placing at Murray Bridge Straight the following run. Has good speed and can quickly clear the tricky draw. Meets a moderate line up and rates on top this time. FREYA LEGEND (4) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 6 lengths at Murray Bridge Straight in a handy 16.88. Has a tricky draw to overcome but has a good record over this journey. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. In sparkling form and expected to measure up again. THUNDERING LADY (1) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fifth wasn't far away finishing 2.75 lengths from the winner (20.28). Boasts a strong record from this draw with four wins and three minor placings from nine starts. Better than last start and can bounce back. CHRISTOFF (2) is right in the mix.",
